### Profiles API Tests
### Variables
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

###############################################
# Profiles APIs (인증 필요)
###############################################

### 내 프로필 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{apiPrefix}}/profiles/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 내 프로필 수정
PUT {{baseUrl}}/{{apiPrefix}}/profiles/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test_user",
  "fullName": "홍길동",
  "avatarUrl": "https://example.com/avatar.jpg"
}

### 내 프로필 수정 (부분 업데이트)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/{{apiPrefix}}/profiles/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "new_username"
}

